summary:
My experience is mentioned within my CV, in my opinion there is really a lot of that.

The good thing about it is I am really flexible person with interest on many fields.

But...
I really would like to settle somewhere and it is not the country I meant specifically but the company and maybe the job position. 

Can be a reliable team member or the manager this depends from the environment that have to work within. Friendly environment with a lot of challenges and comprehensive salary is something that I am looking for.

Specialties: Phone sale and customers support,Hosting Cpanel/Directadmin/Linux administration, Windows administration and support, Wines, Management, Psychology, Dymo support
